now looking at this more as an immediate process rather than a more traditional way it's not even traditional now because it's both ways are taught but traditionally it was about past lives this present life and future life that's why the next one is jati which means birth right but this jati can also be understood as beginning so as soon as you empower something there must be a beginning to the action

